snippet.title: Neon Ships: The Type'em Up Shooter - Trailer
snippet.description:
Shoot enemies while typing pop culture phrases to destroy enemies with your special laser attack! This is a classic Shoot'em up game with a typing twist! We challenge you to dodge all the shots and destroy all the enemies!

Wishlist it now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1528580
